---
title: SuperQuick Chicken-and-Broccoli Rice Bowls with Cheddar Cheese and Green Onions
description: All the flavours of a cheesy chicken and broccoli casserole, but it cooks up in just minutes! Cream cheese adds that cozy and comforting hit of nostalgia.

